1. Potreban mi je *odmor* nakon napornog radnog dana. (I need a *rest* after a long day at work.)
2. Proveli smo dan na *odmoru* na plaži. (We spent the day on *vacation* at the beach.)
3. Planiramo da odemo na *odmor* na planinu. (We plan to go on a *holiday* to the mountains.)
4. Tokom leta, grad je pun turista koji su na *odmoru*. (During the summer, the city is full of tourists who are on *vacation*.)
5. Žao mi je što nisam mogao da dođem na tvoj *odmor*. (I'm sorry I couldn't come to your *holiday*.)
6. Posle završetka školske godine, deca su konačno na *odmoru*. (After the end of the school year, children are finally on *break*.)
7. Koliko *odmora* imaš na poslu? (How many *breaks* do you have at work?)
8. On je trenutno na *odmoru* u inostranstvu. (He is currently on *vacation* abroad.)